Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:21.57,title3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(575,170)\fad(1700,0)}别和往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚實在是萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為補償今天來為各位做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去燒洗澡水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起對不起  真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過難得有機會  要試試扮演小穹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這個你行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以  不要小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:22:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格完全不對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:22:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你是笨蛋桑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不如這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花樣滑冰的空中轉體三周
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個是…百貨店試食區的大嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.44,0:23:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天多謝捧場  歡迎下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.87,0:23:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的總結
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.91,0:23:56.87,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,176)}过犹不及不是杉木樽哦
